Version v3:
Added more details
Added a new trap at the end


It have 2 Terrorist spawns and 64 ct spawns.

20+ traps, some of them I havent seen before on other maps.

Everytime a trap is activated you have a minimum of 30 sec to get past it before the floor breaks but som floors have 60+ seconds.

Fps: 150-200 except at the place with steam, drops to 40 fps couse I have never used that before.
